    <ol class="terms">
        <li>
            1. <u>Scope.</u> This Privacy Policy describes how we handle your personal information for our services available on Rentler.com and on other related sites, tools, applications, or services. By accepting this Privacy Policy and the Terms of Use, you expressly consent to our collection, storage, use and disclosure of your personal information as described in this Privacy Policy, including its transfer to and storage on our servers in the United States or elsewhere in the world. 
        </li>
	    <li>
            2. <u>Collection.</u> While you can use some functions of Rentler.com without being a registered user, certain activities (such as viewing property contact information and advertising a property) do require registration. Once you give us your personal information, you are not anonymous to us. In most cases, the information we hold about you is collected through Rentler.com, but we may also collect information from private-label, co-branded and affiliate websites or their tools, applications or services ("Other Sites"). Depending on the services used, we may collect and store the following personal information:
		    <ul>
			    <li>(a)	contact information such as name, email address, address and telephone number;</li>
			    <li>(b)	move-in date and demographic information such as gender, age, marital status, occupation, and other personal and lifestyle information (for example, if you respond to an optional survey request);</li>
			    <li>(c)	financial information such as credit card or bank account numbers;</li>
			    <li>(d)	additional information we may ask you to send or questions we may ask you to answer to verify your identity (such as your driver's license, credit card statement, and/or a recent utility bill or other information confirming your address);</li>
			    <li>(e) Logs, contact information and other information about the communications between Tenants and Landlords using our communications tools (see Lead Response below).</li>
			    <li></li>
			    <li>(f)	guest card information, lease terms, lease parties and other transactional information; </li>
			    <li>(g)	information based on your interactions with Rentler.com or the Other Sites and their advertising, such as search information, computer sign-on data, statistics on page views, traffic to, from and within Rentler.com or Other Sites, ad data, IP address and standard web log information; and </li>
			    <li>(h)	supplemental information from third parties (for example, if you incur a debt to Rentler.com, we may conduct a credit check by obtaining additional information about you from a credit bureau, as permitted by law). </li>
			    <li>(i)	information about your computer or other access device to mitigate risk and for fraud prevention purposes.</li>
		    </ul>
	    </li>
	    <li>
