		    7.	<u>Third Parties.</u> Except as otherwise expressly included in this Privacy Policy, this document addresses only the use and disclosure of information we collect from you. If you disclose your information to others, whether they are Tenants or Landlords or other sites throughout the Internet, different rules may apply to their use or disclosure of the information you disclose to them. Rentler.com does not control the privacy policies of third parties. We encourage you to ask questions before you disclose your personal information to others. 	
